Founded rotary encoder scripts(not tested).

Make sure that you have python-gpio lib installed. 

If not, can be downloaded here: http://sourceforge.net/projects/raspberry-gpio-python/files/raspbian-wheezy/python-rpi.gpio_0.5.8-1_armhf.deb and installed with  sudo dpkg -i python-rpi.gpio_0.5.8-1_armhf.deb (CHOOSE YOUR RASPBIAN VER.)  

Then copy knob.py to /home/volumio/ ad add path in /etc/rc.local: python /home/volumio/kob.py &  
